VOID ON FRAMEWORK

pre-install:
- create void live installer usb
- make sure everything ready for wipe
- backup previous
  - bak, src, gnupg, ssh, fonts, ref, got, browser tabs & config, accounting, projects
  - any unsynced, orphaned, in-progress tasks, notes
- connect to internet
  - see `ip link` for wifi device name
  - `wpa_passphrase <SSID> <PASSWORD> > /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant-<WIFINAME>.conf`
  - (`wpa_supplicant -B -i <WIFINAME> -c /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant-<WIFINAME>.conf`)
  - (`sv restart dhcpcd`)
  - (`ip link set up <WIFINAME>`)
  - (`dhcpcd <WIFINAME>`)
- partition
  - 1GB /boot/efi (nvme0n1p1)
  - 2GB /boot (nvme0n1p2)
  - rest LUKS + LVM
- LUKS + LVM
  - `cryptsetup luksFormat --hash=sha512 --key-size=512 --cipher=aes-xts-plain64 --verify-passphrase /dev/nvme0n1p3`
  - `cryptsetup open /dev/nvme0n1p3 crypt`
  - `pvcreate /dev/mapper/crypt`
  - `vgcreate box /dev/mapper/crypt`
  - `lvcreate -L 64G box --name swap`
  - `lvcreate -l 100%FREE box --name root`
- format, mount
  - `mkfs.ext4 -L root -m 0.5 /dev/box/root`
  - `mkswap -L swap /dev/box/swap`
  - `mkfs.ext4 -L boot -m 0 /dev/nvme0n1p2`
  - `mkfs.vfat -nEFI /dev/nvme0n1p1`
  - `mount /dev/mapper/box-root /mnt`
  - `mkdir /mnt/boot; mount /dev/nvme0n1p2 /mnt/boot`
  - `mkdir /mnt/efi; mount /dev/nvme0n1p1 /mnt/boot/efi`
  - `swapon /dev/mapper/box-swap`

install:
- installer
  - `void-installer`, follow all steps, install no "Bootloader", skip "Partitions"
  - `xchroot /mnt /bin/bash`
- bootloader
  - `xbps-install -S refind`
  - `refind-install`
  - `vi /boot/refind_linux.conf`
  - `vi /boot/efi/EFI/refind/refind.conf`
- kernel compile
  - `xbps-install -S wget xz base-devel clang llvm cmake extra-cmake-modules {elfutils,ncurses,openssl,xfsprogs}-devel cryptsetup lvm2`
  - `wget cdn.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v6.x/linux-6.16.1.tar.xz`
  - `make CC=clang HOSTCC=clang -j$(nproc)` (oldconfig, menuconfig, make, make modules_install)
    - modular: amdgpu, bt, i2c-hid, i915, !ipv6, iwlwifi, !psmouse, rfcomm, snd
    - fully support: docker, dm-crypt
  - `dracut --force --verbose /boot/initramfs-<VER>.img <VER>`
  - `edit /boot/*/refind*`
    - root=/dev/mapper/box-root add_efi_memmap rd.auto rd.luks=1 rd.luks.uuid=<LUKS_UUID> rd.lvm=1 rd.lvm.vg=box rd.locale.LANG=en_US.UTF-8 rd.md=0 rd.shell rd.vconsole.keymap=hsnt ro
- misc
  - `xbps-install -S bash-completion chrony delta doas fd git iwd socklog-void xtools`
- load backup
  - cfg/opt/: boot, etc, usr

post-reboot:
- enable services
  - `ln -s /etc/sv/? /var/service/` (dbus, dhcpcd, iwd, nanoklogd, ntpd, socklog-unix, uuidd)
- connect to wifi
  - `iwctl`
- load backup:
  - hsnt, bak, bin, cfg, got, opt, ref, src
  - cfg/__shell/: bin
  - cfg/opt/: root
- repos
  - `e /etc/xbps.d/custom.conf`
    - ignorepkg=linux-firmware-nvidia
      repository=https://repo-default.voidlinux.org/current/multilib
      repository=https://repo-default.voidlinux.org/current/multilib/nonfree
      repository=https://repo-default.voidlinux.org/current/nonfree
  - `xbps-install -S`
- apps
  - (sys) acpi, blueman, bolt, clamav, dmidecode, exfatprogs, foot, gotop, gammastep-indicator, gocryptfs, gnupg, hwinfo, intel-media-driver, intel-video-accel, kdeconnect, libva-utils, light, mesa, mesa-dri, mesa-vaapi, mesa-vdpau, mesa-vulkan-intel, mesa-vulkan-radeon, sof-firmware, seatd, thermald, tuigreet, Vulkan-Tools, wev, xorg-server-xwayland, xlsclients, xrdb, xterm
  - (util) elinks, ifuse, kak-lsp, kakoune, lftp, lshw, lz4, lzop, net-tools, ntfs-3g, psmisc, ripgrep, rlwrap, rsync, scrcpy, snooze, socat, stow, tcl, tmux, unzip, xdg-utils, vim, wget, yazi, zip, zstd
  - (devel) base-devel, clang, llvm, cmake, extra-cmake-modules, docker, docker-compose, dive, elixir, gdb, ghc, go, guile, hyperfine, jq, mono, msbuild-bin, n, octave, openjdk, perf, python3-pip, R, rustup, sbcl, squeak, swi-prolog, tcllib, tk, tree, postgresql, postgresql-client, sqlite, nginx, valgrind
  - (wm) breeze-hacked-cursor-theme, chayang, elogind, font-inconsolata-otf, font-sarasa-gothic, freefont-ttf, fuzzel, gnome-keyring, grim, iwgtk, libayatana-appindicator, mako, nautilus, niri, papirus-icon-theme, qt6-wayland, slurp, swappy, swaybg, ttf-opensans, waybar, wl-clipboard, xdg-desktop-portal-gnome, xdg-desktop-portal-gtk, xeyes, xwayland-satellite
    - iwgtk alternative: network-manager-applet
  - (media) ffmpeg, helvum, imv, mpv, pavucontrol, pipewire, wf-recorder, alsa-pipewire, gstreamer1-pipewire, libspa-bluetooth, libspa-ffmpeg, libspa-vulkan
  - (misc) blender, firefox, foliate, fontforge, fontmatrix, geoclue2, gimp, gnucash, gnuplot, ImageMagick, inkscape, krita, libreoffice, pdf.js, qemu, screenkey, texlive-most, tigervnc, ttfautohint, visidata(python3-openpyxl), zathura-{djvu,pdf-mupdf,ps}
  - (manual)
    - google chrome (download .deb file, extract, move to /opt and /usr/local)
    #- niri (git clone and `cargo build --release` with features dbus,xdp-gnome-screencast, version 25.08)
    #  - `xbps-install -S eudev-libudev-devel libxkbcommon-devel libinput-devel libgbm-devel libdisplay-info-devel pipewire-devel pango-devel libseat-devel wayland-devel MesaLib-devel`
    #  - xwayland-satellite (git clone and `cargo build --release`)
    #    - `xbps-install -S libxcb-devel xcb-util-cursor-devel`
  - enable more services (acpid boltd docker greetd polkitd seatd thermald)
  - add to more groups (socklog _clamav _seatd docker)

graphical desktop:
- load home backup: `./stow.tcl`

work:
- `xbps-install -S python3-lsp-server k9s kubectl`
- manual installs
  - aws & kube
    - aws-cli
  - docker
    - `docker login registry.<DOMAIN>.com` (user: username, pass: gitlab token)
  - minio
    - `wget https://dl.min.io/aistor/mc/release/linux-amd64/mc`
  - nodejs
    - `n current`
    - `npm install`
    - `npm install typescript-language-server vscode-{css,html,json}-languageserver-bin`
  - python
    - get miniconda
    - `conda create --name <PROJECT> python=3.??`
    - `conda activate ...`
    - `pip install --user poetry`
    - `poetry config -- http-basic.<PROJECT_GROUP> gitlab-ci-token <TOKEN>`
    - `poetry install`

play:
- steam
  - xdg-user-dirs
  - 32bit: libglapi, libllvm19, libsensors, libXxf86vm, mesa, mesa-dri, mesa-libgallium, mesa-vulkan-intel, mesa-vulkan-radeon xorg-server-xwayland

